text: Mom dad what ARE you doing?
We’re trying to decide what shape we’re in today!
Wow! Can WE do that too?
Of course! Give it a try!
What shape are you in today?
I'm feeling like a circle
I'm a Ferris wheel
A ticking clock The letter O I'm a polka dot!
Hooray! I am a circle! I'm in great shape today!
What shape are you in today?
I'm feeling like a triangle!
I've got three sides

I'm a camping tent An ice cream cone
I’m an instrument!
Hooray! I'm a triangle!
I'm in great shape today
Whatever shapes we may be

Whatever shapes we may be:
Diamond, oval or star
We make the world a wondrous place See how lovely we are!
What shape are you in today?
I'm feeling like a rectangle

I've got four sides
I'm a magazine
A hopscotch court A TV screen!
Hooray! I'm a rectangle! I'm in great shape today
A Pentagon, hexagon Octagon or a heart

Whatever shape you may choose
You're a work of fine art!
What shape are you in today?
I'm feeling like a square
Four sides the same I'm a checkerboard A windowpane
Tiles on the floor Hooray!

I am a square!
I'm in great shape today, yeah
We’re in great shape today
Great shape everyday!
